<doc id="1210917" wikidata="Q5257884" url="?curid=1210917" title="Denjoy integral">
<text>The Denjoy integral in mathematics can refer to two closely related integrals connected to the work of Arnaud Denjoy:

* the &quot;narrow&quot; Denjoy integral, or just Denjoy integral, also known as Henstock–Kurzweil integral,
* the (more general) &quot;wide&quot; Denjoy integral, or Khinchin integral.</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q691340" start="103" end="116" title="Arnaud Denjoy" label="Arnaud Denjoy"/>
