* J.J. Whitlock, How do CANDU reactors meet high safety standards, despite having a &quot;positive void coefficient&quot;? - An explanation published on The Canadian Nuclear FAQ, a website of &quot;frequently-asked questions&quot; and answers about Canadian nuclear technology.</text><links>
