<doc id="1211094" wikidata="Q6782679" url="?curid=1211094" title="Masashi Sugawara">
<text>is a Japanese voice actor who voiced Vigoro in &quot;Skies of Arcadia&quot;, Jean Valjean in &quot;Les Misérables: Shōjo Cosette&quot; and George Joestar in &quot;JoJo&#x27;s Bizarre Adventure&quot;.

